body: @ayush-1506 I am new to open source contribution . This issue is not closed yet . Can I take up this issue .
Sure. You can take up any issue that doesn't have a PR open against it.

Yep, sure. Feel free to work on this. (As I mentioned above, you can work on any issue that doesn't have a PR open against it.)
